File & Code Handling
JSZip (free) — Generate zip downloads of project files (Issue #4)
FileSaver.js (free) — Trigger browser download of the zip
Prettier (free) — Auto-format generated code before showing user
ESLint (free) — Lint generated code in your sandbox test step
@typescript-eslint (free) — TypeScript-specific linting for generated code
tree-sitter (free, WASM) — Parse and analyze generated code AST for the Critic agent
Babel (free) — Transform/validate JS in browser
